## Part 1

```elixir
races
|> Enum.map(fn {time, distance} ->
  1..(time - 1)
  |> Enum.drop_while(fn n -> n * (time - n) <= distance end)
  |> Enum.take_while(fn n -> n * (time - n) > distance end)
  |> Enum.count()
end)
|> Enum.product()
